Notes.Text:
This update for libqt5-qtbase fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-32763: Fixed an overflow in QTextLayout (bsc#1211798).

Vulnerabilities.Description: An issue was discovered in Qt before 5.15.15, 6.x before 6.2.9, and 6.3.x through 6.5.x before 6.5.1. When a SVG file with an image inside it is rendered, a QTextLayout buffer overflow can be triggered.
